Shoppie Website
Welcome to the Shoppie website! This website serves as an admin panel for managing products and users. It provides functionality for uploading products, viewing all products, and managing user data.
It also enables users to search for products, add/remove from cart, checkout and view the shop. The website is designed to work on various screen sizes.

